%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch-chu-trung/poem-PMdDGuheRxm6e6ZPv_Twnw">Thất tịch chu trung - 七夕舟中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-OTOkL6TRbM0V41YwHIzvfA">Xà Tường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/Thu-m%E1%BB%99ng/poem-ORohNpqjZesYWNw-yFqdWg">Thu mộng - 秋夢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/T%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-QJK74_J02inWJMEPxc2HOg">Tự thán kỳ 2 - 自歎其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/author-7tg_rhleFYVL5Ann2EB2iA">Trần Danh Án</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-hi%E1%BB%83u-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-4n45ck7MJYBO7iOXAoJ86A">Tương hiểu kỳ 1 - 將曉其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-Kh%E1%BA%A5u/V%C3%A3n-Ho%C3%A0-Th%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-2FWFWx4EuGpm8IutnZctMA">Vãn Hoà Thân kỳ 2 - 挽和珅其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-Kh%E1%BA%A5u/author-svMQDOV_e4vEtYCGO8gq1g">Đậu Khấu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-ge9IfP4qAzGhQhdEqnXX9g">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
